-- Valeant again boosts cash in offer for Allergan
-- By Rod Nickel in Winnipeg
-- Fri May 30, 2014 02:48PM EDT
-- None



May 30 (Reuters) - Valeant Pharmaceuticals International Inc <VRX.TO> said on Friday that it would increase the cash component in its takeover bid for Botox-maker Allergan Inc <AGN.N> for the second time this week, contingent on the two sides negotiating.

